    "description": "Lillysia 是一款 2D 平台游戏，您的旅程是为生病的宠物提供疫苗。<br>当你跳起来撞墙时，你可以下推着陆或打破障碍。<br>您必须使用这些操作来克服您面临的障碍。<br>当你犯错时，你可以再试一次并学习如何避免错误。<br><br><strong>游戏玩法</strong><br>1.按住按钮并松开进行跳远。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176030/extras/20ad60caf2b266e98bc470421997e01b.poster.avif?t=1752827800\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176030/extras/20ad60caf2b266e98bc470421997e01b.webm?t=1752827800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176030/extras/20ad60caf2b266e98bc470421997e01b.mp4?t=1752827800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>2.跳跃撞墙时，有几率使用一次下推，<br>此动作用于打破障碍或跳跃着陆。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176030/extras/e557f040073ab208ac57f9e119c44644.poster.avif?t=1752827800\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176030/extras/e557f040073ab208ac57f9e119c44644.webm?t=1752827800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176030/extras/e557f040073ab208ac57f9e119c44644.mp4?t=1752827800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>3.骑在鸟身上会让你跳得更高。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176030/extras/0c4d43969131fbd885cbc949ee7473e1.poster.avif?t=1752827800\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176030/extras/0c4d43969131fbd885cbc949ee7473e1.webm?t=1752827800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176030/extras/0c4d43969131fbd885cbc949ee7473e1.mp4?t=1752827800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>4.下压鸟时的最大跳跃距离。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176030/extras/59a64b070a45e881c02e2d619e3548f1.poster.avif?t=1752827800\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176030/extras/59a64b070a45e881c02e2d619e3548f1.webm?t=1752827800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176030/extras/59a64b070a45e881c02e2d619e3548f1.mp4?t=1752827800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>5.自动保存每个阶段。",
